---
// Proposal for Sky Pups Treats — not linked from nav, shared directly with client
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>A Website Proposal for Sky Pups Treats — Brandon Woodward</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --green:  #2D6A4F;
      --salmon: #E07A5F;
      --text:   #1A1A1A;
      --dim:    #4A4A4A;
      --muted:  #6B6B6B;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      --bg:     #FAFAF7;
      --surface:#F0EDE8;
      --font-body: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      --font-hand: 'Caveat', cursive;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; }

    body {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 5rem;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      body { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    }

    .letter-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .sender-name  { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .sender-title { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    .sender-contact { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .sender-contact a { color: var(--green); text-decoration: none; }
    .letter-date { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); text-align: right; }

    .addressee { margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.7; }

    .greeting { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

    p { font-size: 0.915rem; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
    p strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    .demo-box {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.25);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--green);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .demo-box-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .demo-box h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    .demo-url { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--green); }
    .demo-url a { color: var(--green); text-decoration: none; }
    .demo-url a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .demo-creds { display: flex; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 0.9rem; }
    .demo-cred  { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .demo-cred strong {
      display: block; font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .demo-cred span { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    .offer-box {
      background: var(--green); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0; color: #fff;
    }

    .offer-box-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .offer-box h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }

    .offer-price {
      font-family: var(--font-hand); font-size: 2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .offer-box p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-bottom: 0; }

    .includes-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; margin: 1.25rem 0; }

    .includes-list li {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .includes-list li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.05rem; }

    .next-steps { background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .next-steps h3 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .next-step-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .next-step { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--dim); }
    .next-step a { color: var(--green); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    .next-step a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .closing { margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--dim); }
    .signature { font-family: var(--font-hand); font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
    .sig-name { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.25rem; }

    .ps-section {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .ps-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .ps-intro {
      font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 1.75rem; font-style: italic;
    }

    .dog-testimonials { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

    .dog-review {
      display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start;
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem;
    }

    .dog-photo {
      width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover; flex-shrink: 0;
      border: 3px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.2);
    }

    .dog-review-body { flex: 1; }

    .dog-stars { color: #D4960A; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

    .dog-quote {
      font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.7;
      font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .dog-name {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .dog-title { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.1rem; }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .dog-review { flex-direction: column; }
      .dog-photo { width: 56px; height: 56px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="letter-header">
    <div>
      <div class="sender-name">Brandon Woodward</div>
      <div class="sender-title">Systems Architect &amp; Web Consultant</div>
      <div class="sender-contact">
        <a href="mailto:brandon@woodhead.tech">brandon@woodhead.tech</a><br />
        <a href="https://woodhead.tech">woodhead.tech</a><br />
        <a href="https://cal.com/brandon-woodward-3nlfbd">cal.com/brandon-woodward-3nlfbd</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="letter-date">May 17, 2026</div>
  </div>

  <div class="addressee">
    Michele &amp; Chris<br />
    Sky Pups Treats<br />
    1202 NE 98th Street<br />
    Seattle, WA 98115
  </div>

  <p class="greeting">Hi Michele and Chris,</p>

  <p>
    I picked up some freeze-dried chicken jerky at your booth a few weeks ago. My dogs London, Bob Barker,
    and Ollie gave it an enthusiastic review — they were pushing each other out of the way before I could get the
    bag open. I'm a convert.
  </p>

  <p>
    I'm a systems and web consultant based here in Seattle, and I'd love to offer you something: <strong>a
    redesigned website, hosted reliably on Amazon Web Services, for $100/month</strong> — just enough to
    cover the AWS infrastructure costs. The design and build work would be on me, in exchange for the
    opportunity to use the project as a case study.
  </p>

  <p>
    Here's why I'm reaching out. The thing that struck me most about your booth wasn't the treats — it
    was the signed packages. The handwritten thank-you with your names and Sky and Bear's names. That
    detail tells the whole story of what you're doing: a family that cares, making something real for
    people who care about their dogs. <strong>Your current website doesn't tell that story the way you do
    in person.</strong>
  </p>

  <div class="demo-box">
    <div class="demo-box-label">I built you a preview</div>
    <h3>Your new website is already live — take a look:</h3>
    <div class="demo-url"><a href="https://skypups.woodhead.tech">https://skypups.woodhead.tech</a></div>
    <div class="demo-creds">
      <div class="demo-cred">
        <strong>Username</strong>
        <span>skypups</span>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-cred">
        <strong>Password</strong>
        <span>pnwpups2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    I built it on the same technology stack I use for my own consulting business — Astro,
    a modern static site framework, hosted on AWS. It loads fast, looks great on mobile, and is
    designed specifically around your brand: the Pacific Northwest sourcing, the single-ingredient
    commitment, the family story, and especially that signature.
  </p>

  <p>
    The problem I want to help you solve is simple: <strong>slow IT response costs you real money.</strong>
    Every time you launch a new batch or sell out of something, your website should reflect that same
    day — not next week when your IT person gets around to it. When a new farmer's market date goes on
    the calendar, your followers should know immediately. With me managing your site, changes happen
    within 24 hours. Usually same day.
  </p>

  <div class="offer-box">
    <div class="offer-box-label">The offer</div>
    <h3>Introductory Partnership Rate</h3>
    <div class="offer-price">$100 / month</div>
    <p>
      This covers your AWS hosting costs. The design, build, and my time are free —
      in exchange for a testimonial and permission to share your story as a case study on my website.
      You get a professional, fast-loading website with no upfront cost. I get a client I'm proud to work with.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p><strong>What's included:</strong></p>
  <ul class="includes-list">
    <li>Fully redesigned website (Home, Products, About, Contact) — built on modern, fast technology</li>
    <li>Hosted on Amazon Web Services — reliable, scales automatically, never goes down on a busy market day</li>
    <li>Your own domain (skypupstreats.com) pointing to the new site</li>
    <li>Content updates within 24 hours of your request — new products, pricing, market dates, anything</li>
    <li>Monthly check-in to make sure everything is working the way you need it</li>
    <li>No contracts, no lock-in — cancel anytime with 30 days notice</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    I should be honest: this is my first client engagement, and that's exactly why I'm offering my
    time for free. I want to do great work for someone whose product I genuinely respect, and build
    a track record I can point to. You'd be doing me a favor by saying yes.
  </p>

  <div class="next-steps">
    <h3>Ready to talk?</h3>
    <div class="next-step-items">
      <div class="next-step">📅 &nbsp;<span>Schedule a 20-minute Google Meet: <a href="https://cal.com/brandon-woodward-3nlfbd">cal.com/brandon-woodward-3nlfbd</a></span></div>
      <div class="next-step">📧 &nbsp;<span>Email: <a href="mailto:brandon@woodhead.tech">brandon@woodhead.tech</a></span></div>
      <div class="next-step">📞 &nbsp;<span>Call or text: <a href="tel:4253442942">(425) 344-2942</a></span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    Thanks for making treats my dogs love. London, Bob Barker, and Ollie are very much looking forward to
    a continued relationship.
  </p>

  <div class="closing">
    Warmly,
    <div class="signature">Brandon Woodward</div>
    <div class="sig-name">Systems Architect &amp; Web Consultant — Seattle, WA</div>
  </div>

  <div class="ps-section">
    <div class="ps-label">P.S. — Independent Expert Opinion</div>
    <p class="ps-intro">
      Three independent reviewers. No treats were withheld in exchange for positive coverage.
    </p>

    <div class="dog-testimonials">

      <div class="dog-review">
        <img src="/proposals/bob-barker.jpg" alt="London" class="dog-photo" />
        <div class="dog-review-body">
          <div class="dog-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="dog-quote">
            "I rate this treat 5 out of 5 paws. When my human opened the bag, I became so excited that I knocked him
            directly into the kitchen cabinet. He said something under his breath. I did not hear it. I was focused
            on the chicken jerky. The chicken jerky was worth it. I would do it again. I will do it again."
          </p>
          <div class="dog-name">London</div>
          <div class="dog-title">Professional Good Girl · Enthusiast · Seattle, WA</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dog-review">
        <img src="/proposals/ollie.jpg" alt="Ollie" class="dog-photo" />
        <div class="dog-review-body">
          <div class="dog-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="dog-quote">
            "It was my birthday. My human gave me a Sky Pups chicken jerky treat. I closed my eyes. I let the chicken
            wash over me. In that moment, I understood something about myself. Something about life. I am changed.
            I am better. I am Ollie. My only feedback: more of them."
          </p>
          <div class="dog-name">Ollie</div>
          <div class="dog-title">Snack Enthusiast · Birthday Boy · Golden Mix · Seattle, WA</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dog-review">
        <img src="/proposals/critic.jpg" alt="Bob Barker" class="dog-photo" />
        <div class="dog-review-body">
          <div class="dog-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="dog-quote">
            "I was skeptical. I am always skeptical. That is my job. I inspected the packaging. I inspected the
            ingredients. I took a single careful bite. I considered the bite. I took six more bites. I am still
            skeptical in general. About these treats, however, I have no notes. They passed."
          </p>
          <div class="dog-name">Bob Barker</div>
          <div class="dog-title">Senior Snack Inspector · Certified Skeptic · Seattle, WA</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
